graph TB
    subgraph "Data Science Pipelines Operator"
        Controller[DSPO Controller<br/>Operator]
        ControllerMetrics[Metrics Endpoint<br/>8080/TCP]
        Controller -->|exposes| ControllerMetrics
    end

    subgraph "DSPA Instance Components (per namespace)"
        direction TB

        APIServer[DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP, 8887/TCP gRPC<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS OAuth]
        PersistenceAgent[Persistence Agent<br/>Syncs workflow state]
        ScheduledWorkflow[Scheduled Workflow Controller<br/>Cron management]
        WorkflowController[Argo Workflow Controller<br/>Namespace-scoped]

        subgraph "Optional Components"
            MariaDB[(MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP<br/>TLS)]
            Minio[(Minio<br/>9000/TCP<br/>S3 API)]
            MLMDgRPC[ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP]
            MLMDEnvoy[MLMD Envoy Proxy<br/>9090/TCP]
        end

        APIServer -->|writes metadata| MariaDB
        APIServer -->|creates workflows| WorkflowController
        APIServer -->|queries lineage| MLMDgRPC
        PersistenceAgent -->|syncs state| MariaDB
        PersistenceAgent -->|watches workflows| WorkflowController
        ScheduledWorkflow -->|creates runs| APIServer
        WorkflowController -->|executes| PipelinePods
        MLMDEnvoy -->|proxies| MLMDgRPC
        MLMDgRPC -->|stores metadata| MariaDB

        PipelinePods[Pipeline Execution Pods]
        PipelinePods -->|reads/writes artifacts| Minio
        PipelinePods -->|reads/writes artifacts| ExternalS3
        PipelinePods -->|tracks lineage| MLMDEnvoy
        PipelinePods -->|reports status| APIServer
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| DSPACR[DataSciencePipelinesApplication CR]
    DSPACR -->|watched by| Controller
    Controller -->|deploys| APIServer
    Controller -->|deploys| PersistenceAgent
    Controller -->|deploys| ScheduledWorkflow
    Controller -->|deploys| WorkflowController
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| MariaDB
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| Minio
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| MLMDgRPC
    Controller -->|optionally deploys| MLMDEnvoy

    subgraph "External Services"
        ExternalS3[External S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>AWS IAM Auth]
        ExternalDB[(External Database<br/>3306/5432 TCP<br/>TLS)]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]
    end

    Controller -->|manages resources| K8sAPI
    WorkflowController -->|creates pods| K8sAPI
    APIServer -.->|alternative DB| ExternalDB
    PipelinePods -.->|production storage| ExternalS3

    subgraph "Integration Points"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI Integration]
        Workbenches[Workbenches/Notebooks<br/>Pipeline authoring]
        KServe[KServe<br/>Model deployment]
        RayClusters[Ray Clusters<br/>Distributed compute]
    end

    Dashboard -->|UI API calls| APIServer
    Workbenches -->|submit pipelines| APIServer
    PipelinePods -->|deploys models| KServe
    PipelinePods -->|distributed tasks| RayClusters

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style APIServer fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PersistenceAgent fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ScheduledWorkflow fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style WorkflowController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSPACR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MariaDB fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Minio fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style MLMDgRPC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style MLMDEnvoy fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style ExternalS3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style ExternalDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Workbenches fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style RayClusters fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
